  "name": "Loan Document Intelligence Agent",
  "description": "A unified AI agent that manages the full lifecycle of syndicated loan document processing. It ingests credit agreements (PDF/DOCX), extracts loan reference data including SOFR and floating rate instruments, validates against the Loan Administration System, reconciles discrepancies, routes exceptions to operations teams, and emits a data quality report — all in a single orchestrated workflow with built-in immutable audit logging.",
  "preferredTransport": "JSONRPC",
  "protocol_version": "0.3.0",
